refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arrayposix_getgrnam stringname
Gets information about a group provided its name.

  &reftitle.parameters;




     name


The name of the group

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     4.2.0

      Prior to this version, members was simply an integer representing the
      number of members in the group, and the member names were returned
      with numerical indices.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Example use of posix_getgrnam


<?php

$groupinfo = posix_getgrnam("toons");

print_r($groupinfo);
?>


    &example.outputs.similar;


Array
(
    [name]    => toons
    [passwd]  => x
    [members] => Array
        (
            [0] => tom
            [1] => jerry
        )
    [gid]     => 42
)
